WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.555
Bardéla is elected president of the national restaurant

00:00:04.044 --> 00:00:06.482
Bardéla succeeds Marine Le Pen

00:00:06.483 --> 00:00:08.279
at the head of the national gathering

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:09.455
far right party

00:00:09.456 --> 00:00:12.045
he was widely elected by rn members

00:00:12.046 --> 00:00:12.975
with nearly 85

00:00:13.304 --> 00:00:14.567
votes on November 5

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:16.959
at 27 years old he has comfortably imposed himself

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:18.091
in front of the mayor of Perp

00:00:18.092 --> 00:00:19.828
louis aliot who collected only 15

00:00:19.931 --> 00:00:21.281
16 of the votes

00:00:21.371 --> 00:00:22.989
much appreciated by members

00:00:22.990 --> 00:00:24.549
Charles Bardella was the favorite

00:00:24.550 --> 00:00:26.948
thanks in particular to his background in the party

00:00:27.250 --> 00:00:29.089
native of drancy in seine saint denis

00:00:29.170 --> 00:00:30.229
Bardella

00:00:30.230 --> 00:00:32.069
grew up in a family of Italian origin

00:00:32.150 --> 00:00:32.859
he is 16 years old

00:00:32.860 --> 00:00:35.109
when he joined the national front in February 2012

00:00:35.170 --> 00:00:37.049
the ancestor of the national gathering

00:00:37.150 --> 00:00:38.369
and in about ten years

00:00:38.370 --> 00:00:39.756
he quickly climbs the ladder

00:00:39.757 --> 00:00:41.186
under the leadership of marine le pen

00:00:41.350 --> 00:00:42.224
good little soldier

00:00:42.270 --> 00:00:44.449
he goes through the positions of party secretary

00:00:44.790 --> 00:00:45.764
of spokesperson

00:00:46.120 --> 00:00:47.789
then director of Generation Nation

00:00:47.790 --> 00:00:49.779
the orn youth affiliate movement

00:00:49.780 --> 00:00:50.339
then

00:00:50.340 --> 00:00:52.519
he becomes a leader in the European elections

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:54.069
and takes the interim presidency

00:00:54.070 --> 00:00:56.074
during the presidential marine campaign le pen

00:00:56.440 --> 00:00:57.884
although he is close to the family circle

00:00:58.135 --> 00:01:00.252
he is the first one who does not have the name le pen

00:01:00.295 --> 00:01:02.769
to assume the presidency of the rn because before him

00:01:02.770 --> 00:01:05.192
it was marine le pen and his father jean marie le pen

00:01:05.193 --> 00:01:06.264
who held the reins of the party
